						<summary>

						<p>Slab built as a step to the shop of Irasangappa in the bazaar.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">12th century A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>The record engraved on two faces of the slab is worn out. The purport of the extant portion is not clear.</p>						

						<p>It is in characters of the 12th century A.D.</p>						

